Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【製作名單】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}片源提供:{\fscx90}Zhq
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}對白翻譯:蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}對白校對:灰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}繁體校正:{\fscx90}simon_9331
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}字幕計時:{\fscx90}kilyao
